"en": "No one knows his true identity and origin. He always appears at critical moments, giving people mysterious guidance. Some say he is a prophet, some say he is a hermit.",
"zh": "没有人知道他的真实身份和来历。他总是出现在关键时刻，给予人们神秘的指引。有人说他是预言家，有人说他是隐士。"
}
